        IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
        PROGRAM-ID. MEE5377F.
        DATA DIVISION.
        WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
        01 RPT-RECORD.
          05 RPT-REC PIC X(2000).
        01 RPT-RECORD1 REDEFINES RPT-RECORD.
          05 RPT-REC1 PIC X(1).
        01 WS-RPT-LENGTH PIC 9(5).
        LINKAGE SECTION.
        01 COMMON-LINKAGE-SECTION.
          05 RPT-LINK-RECORD.
            10 RPT-LINK-LENGTH PIC S9(5) COMP.
            10 RPT-LINK-REST PIC X(2000).
        PROCEDURE DIVISION USING COMMON-LINKAGE-SECTION.
            COMPUTE WS-RPT-LENGTH = RPT-LINK-LENGTH - 4
            IF RPT-LINK-LENGTH > 0 THEN
                IF RPT-LINK-LENGTH < 2000 THEN
                    MOVE RPT-LINK-REST(1:WS-RPT-LENGTH)
                         TO RPT-RECORD(1:WS-RPT-LENGTH)
                    DISPLAY RPT-LINK-LENGTH
                    DISPLAY RPT-RECORD(1:WS-RPT-LENGTH) '|'
                END-IF
            END-IF

            GOBACK.
